    "body": "This sounds like a good proposal and it seems your solution is good as well. So just to re-iterate, my understanding of this proposal is that we will be adding the capability to input an object containing `mnemonic` and `password` keys during instantiation which will be used to generate the seed and thus create the addresses.\r\n\r\nAlso, do you maybe have some old code that you copied from in your code sample? I'm not sure what the `kdkey_1.default` business is. :) This is the relevant code https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/hdwallet-provider/src/index.ts#L73-L91.\r\n\r\nAlso I want to see if @gnidan has any objection to this.",
